headline: Carnival Reshapes Listing Structure With Bermuda Move And New Name
summary: Carnival Corporation & plans to unify its New York and London listings into a single structure. The company intends to redomicile to Bermuda and operate under a new name, Carnival Corporation Ltd. This move represents a structural shift in how NYSE:CCL is organized and traded in global capital markets. headline: Holland America Line and Crane Stationery Celebrate America's 250th with Veteran‑Designed Cards Honoring the Written Word
summary: Holland America Line is partnering with Crane, the renowned American stationery brand, to commemorate America's 250th anniversary with an original collection of cards designed by artists from the United States Veterans' Artists Alliance (USVAA). Rooted in the storied legacies of Crane and Holland America Line, these exclusive, original designs honor heritage shaped over generations.
